Privacy Policy
Last updated:
October 21st, 2021
.
1.0 Information We Collect
The Deliveries Tracker App is committed to protecting the privacy of its users. We do not collect any personal data from our users, nor do we track any user data. We do not share or sell any user information to third parties.
We only collect and store the information necessary to provide our services, such as delivery details and tracking information. This information is kept secure and is only accessible by authorized personnel within our company.
1.1 Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and by showing a message in the app. These changes are effective immediately after they are posted on this page.
1.2 Contact Us
If you have any questions or suggestions about our Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us at
